用小狼毫，准备类似 Mac 一个简约一些的皮肤
虽然说比起原版还是有很大的差异，比如说，没有阴影，边框颜色有问题等，以下是代码，需要放在小狼毫用户文件夹的"weasel.custom.yaml"中
```text
patch:
  style:
    color_scheme: succulent_plant
    font_face: HarmonyOS Sans SC
    font_point: 12
    horizontal: true
    fullscreen: false
    inline_preedit: true
    preedit_type: composition
    display_tray_icon: true
    label_format: '%s'
    layout:
      min_width: 100
      min_height: 0
      border_width: 1
      margin_x: 5
      margin_y: 5
      spacing: 10
      candidate_spacing: 10
      hilite_spacing: 5
      hilite_padding: 3
      round_corner: 7
  preset_color_schemes/succulent_plant:
    name: simple
    author: zzh
    back_color: '0xffffff'
    border_color: '0xc8dad9'
    text_color: '0xffffff'
    hilited_text_color: '0xffffff'
    hilited_back_color: '0xc95d2f'
    hilited_comment_text_color: '0xffffff'
    hilited_candidate_text_color: '0xffffff'
    hilited_candidate_back_color: '0xc95d2f'
    hilited_label_color: '0xffffff'
    candidate_text_color: '0x424242'
    comment_text_color: '0x000000'
    label_color: '0x7d7d7d'
```
